    'featured_listings.AdditionalTermsForFeaturedAds': 'Papildu termini reklam\u0113tajiem sludin\u0101jumiem',
    'featured_listings.AdditionalTermsForFeaturedAds_content': '\u0160ie papildu termini t\u012Bmek\u013Ca vietnes <<LINK_TERMS_USE>>Terminiem<</LINK_TERMS_USE>> ir saist\u012Bti ar reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu izmanto\u0161anu:<br /><ul><li>Par pier\u0101d\u012Bjumu samaksai par reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu, OLX izdos tikai \u201CPas\u016Bt\u012Bjuma apstiprin\u0101jumu\u201D, ko j\u016Bs ieraudz\u012Bsiet maks\u0101\u0161anas procesa beig\u0101s, k\u0101 ar\u012B apstiprin\u0101jumu pa e-pastu.  </li><li>Ja k\u0101da iemesla d\u0113\u013C, tehniska vai k\u0101da cita, j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101jums nepar\u0101d\u0101s \u201CReklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu\u201D zon\u0101, OLXvien\u012Bg\u0101 atbild\u012Bba aprobe\u017Eojas ar j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101juma p\u0113c iesp\u0113jas \u0101tr\u0101ku ievieto\u0161anu \u201CReklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu\u201D zon\u0101.</li><li>Cits pakalpojumu sniedz\u0113js, darbodamies k\u0101 tre\u0161\u0101 puse, nodro\u0161ina r\u0113\u0137inu apstr\u0101di.</li><li>Vien\u012Bgi p\u0113c OLXvienpus\u012Bga ieskata, jebk\u0101di aizskaro\u0161i, pornogr\u0101fiski, kr\u0101pnieciski (tai skait\u0101, kop\u0113ti sludin\u0101jumi), potenci\u0101li kr\u0101pnieciski vai autorties\u012Bbas p\u0101rk\u0101pjo\u0161i sludin\u0101jumi netiek reklam\u0113ti, un samaks\u0101t\u0101 nauda netiek atmaks\u0101ta.</li><li>\u0160IS SLUDIN\u0100JUMU REKL\u0100MAS PAKALPOJUMS TIEK PIED\u0100V\u0100TS TIKAI T\u0100DS, K\u0100DS TAS IR, BEZ JEBK\u0100D\u0100M GARANTIJ\u0100M, CIKT\u0100L TO PIE\u013BAUJ LIKUMS.  OLX NEDOD NEK\u0100DAS GARANTIJAS VAI GALVOJUMUS UN NEUZ\u0145EMAS NEK\u0100DAS SAIST\u012ABAS VAI ATBILD\u012ABU PAR AR REKLAM\u0112T\u0100 SLUDIN\u0100JUMA PAKALPOJUMA PAL\u012ADZ\u012ABU PUBLIC\u0112T\u0100 SLUDIN\u0100JUMA PRECIZIT\u0100TI VAI PILN\u012ABU.</li></ul>',
    'featured_listings.Benefits': 'Priek\u0161roc\u012Bbas',
    'featured_listings.Benefits_content': 'J\u016Bsu sludin\u0101juma atra\u0161an\u0101s vieta b\u016Bs lab\u0101ka, ja tas par\u0101d\u012Bsies reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu noda\u013C\u0101s, kas aprakst\u012Btas zem\u0101k.Zem\u0101k redzamajos att\u0113los par\u0101d\u012Bti divi iesp\u0113jamie reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu veidi.',
    'featured_listings.Feature': 'Rekl\u0101ma',
    'featured_listings.FeaturedListings_Content': 'Reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu pakalpojums \u013Cauj j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101jumu par\u0101d\u012Bt reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu noda\u013C\u0101s, kas nodro\u0161ina l\u012Bdz pat 20 reiz\u0113m liel\u0101ku j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101juma redzam\u012Bbu, sal\u012Bdzinot ar parastu sludin\u0101jumu!',
    'featured_listings.FeatureMyListing': 'Reklam\u0113t manu sludin\u0101jumu',
    'featured_listings.FeatureYourListingForUp20TimesVisibility': '<<LINK_FEATURED_LISTINGS>>Reklam\u0113jiet savu sludin\u0101jumu<</LINK_FEATURED_LISTINGS>>, lai t\u0101 redzam\u012Bba vietn\u0113 b\u016Btu 20 reizes liel\u0101ka!',
    'featured_listings.HowDoesItWork': 'K\u0101 tas darbojas?',
    'featured_listings.HowDoesItWork_New': 'Attiec\u012Bb\u0101 uz sludin\u0101jumu saraksta aug\u0161galu un mekl\u0113\u0161anas rezult\u0101tos reklam\u0113tiem sludin\u0101jumiem - reklam\u0113tie sludin\u0101jumi tiek r\u0101d\u012Bti piem\u0113rot\u0101 kategorij\u0101 un tiek nejau\u0161\u0101 k\u0101rt\u012Bb\u0101 "rot\u0113ti" starp \u0161\u012Bs kategorijas un vietas reklam\u0113tajiem sludin\u0101jumiem. Jebkur\u0101 gad\u012Bjum\u0101, reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu atlase ir nejau\u0161a, lai dotu visiem reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu pakalpojuma pirc\u0113jiem vien\u0101du iesp\u0113ju tikt paman\u012Btiem t\u012Bmek\u013Ca vietn\u0113. T\u0101p\u0113c var b\u016Bt t\u0101, ka j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101jums neb\u016Bs past\u0101v\u012Bgi redzams attiec\u012Bgaj\u0101 reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu sada\u013C\u0101.',
    'featured_listings.HowDoIBuyAFeaturedListing': 'K\u0101 es varu ieg\u0101d\u0101ties reklam\u0113tu sludin\u0101jumu?',
    'featured_listings.HowDoIBuyAFeaturedListing_New': 'Sludin\u0101jumu reklam\u0113\u0161anas pakalpojumu j\u016Bs varat nopirkt public\u0113\u0161anas procesa p\u0113d\u0113j\u0101 sol\u012B, kur\u0101 tiek apstiprin\u0101ts, ka j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101jums ir public\u0113ts, vai ar\u012B no My OLX. Process nav sare\u017E\u0123\u012Bts. Izv\u0113lieties, cik ned\u0113\u013Cas ilgi v\u0113laties savu sludin\u0101jumu reklam\u0113t. P\u0113c tam j\u016Bs non\u0101ksiet maks\u0101\u0161anas lap\u0101, kur\u0101 ir da\u017E\u0101das maks\u0101jumu veik\u0161anas iesp\u0113jas. P\u0113c maks\u0101juma izdar\u012B\u0161anas j\u016Bs sa\u0146emsiet apstiprin\u0101jumu, ka j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101jums ir pieejams izv\u0113l\u0113taj\u0101 laika period\u0101. Ja j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101jums atbilst OLX lieto\u0161anas noteikumiem, j\u016Bs sa\u0146emsiet apstiprin\u0101jumu pa e-pastu.  L\u016Bdzu, \u0146emiet v\u0113r\u0101, ka nav iesp\u0113jama nek\u0101da naudas atgrie\u0161ana, ja b\u016Bsiet nopircis sludin\u0101jumu reklam\u0113\u0161anas pakalpojumu. Reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu pakalpojuma pirk\u0161anas dar\u012Bjums ir gal\u012Bgs.',
    'featured_listings.HowDoIFeatureMyAd': 'K\u0101 es varu reklam\u0113t savu sludin\u0101jumu?',
    'featured_listings.HowLongWillMyListingAppearInFeaturedListings': 'Cik ilgi mans sludin\u0101jums par\u0101d\u012Bsies reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu sada\u013C\u0101?',
    'featured_listings.HowLongWillMyListingAppearInFeaturedListings_content': 'Reklam\u0113tie sludin\u0101jumi tiek p\u0101rdoti uz ned\u0113\u013Cu (7 dien\u0101m). Varat reklam\u0113t savu sludin\u0101jumu l\u012Bdz pat 4 ned\u0113\u013C\u0101m.',
