    'featured_listings.HowMuchDoesItCost_New': 'Sludin\u0101jums saraksta aug\u0161gal\u0101 un mekl\u0113jumu rezult\u0101tos reklam\u0113ts sludin\u0101jums maks\u0101 <<LISTING_OTHER_CATS_FEATURED_PRICE>> ned\u0113\u013C\u0101..J\u016Bs varat izv\u0113l\u0113ties, cik ilgi v\u0113laties reklam\u0113t savu sludin\u0101jumu saraksta aug\u0161gal\u0101 un mekl\u0113jumu rezult\u0101tos, bet ne ilg\u0101k par 4 ned\u0113\u013C\u0101m.',
    'featured_listings.HowMuchVisitsWillIncrease': 'Cik liel\u0101 m\u0113r\u0101 palielin\u0101sies mana sludin\u0101juma apl\u016Bko\u0161anas bie\u017Eums?',
    'featured_listings.HowMuchVisitsWillIncrease_content': 'Reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu m\u0113r\u0137is ir palielin\u0101t j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101juma redzam\u012Bbu.  Vid\u0113ji ir 8 reizes vair\u0101k cilv\u0113ku, kas tos apl\u016Bko, sal\u012Bdzin\u0101jum\u0101 ar parastajiem sludin\u0101jumiem. Taj\u0101s kategorij\u0101s, kur\u0101s ir visliel\u0101kais sludin\u0101jumu skaits, reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu redzam\u012Bba var palielin\u0101ties pat 20 reizes.*',
    'featured_listings.IDontSeeMyListingInFeaturedListings': 'Es neredzu savu sludin\u0101jumu reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu zon\u0101.',
    'featured_listings.IDontSeeMyListingInFeaturedListings_content': 'Ja esat ieg\u0101d\u0101jies reklam\u0113tu sludin\u0101jumu un neredzat to  \u0161im sludin\u0101jumam paredz\u0113taj\u0101 zon\u0101, l\u016Bdzu:<br /><ul><li>P\u0101rbaudiet, vai esat sa\u0146\u0113mis apstiprin\u0101juma e-v\u0113stuli, ka j\u016Bsu reklam\u0113tais sludin\u0101jums ir redzams tie\u0161saist\u0113. Sludin\u0101juma apstiprin\u0101\u0161anai nepiecie\u0161amais laiks var b\u016Bt l\u012Bdz 24 stund\u0101m.</li><li>P\u0101rbaudiet sava reklam\u0113t\u0101 sludin\u0101juma s\u0101kuma un beigu datumus, kas nor\u0101d\u012Bti apstiprin\u0101juma e-v\u0113stul\u0113.</li><li>Atcerieties, ka j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101jums atrodas \u201Crot\u0101cij\u0101\u201D ar citiem t\u0101s pa\u0161as kategorijas sludin\u0101jumiem attiec\u012Bgaj\u0101 atra\u0161an\u0101s viet\u0101, t\u0101d\u0113\u013C tas neb\u016Bs redzams visu laiku. K\u0101 likums, dienas laik\u0101 tiks par\u0101d\u012Bti ne vair\u0101k k\u0101 18 k\u0101das kategorijas "rot\u0101cij\u0101" iek\u013Cautie sludin\u0101jumi attiec\u012Bgaj\u0101 pils\u0113t\u0101, t\u0101d\u0113\u013C j\u016Bsu sludin\u0101jums b\u016Bs redzams sludin\u0101jumu aug\u0161da\u013C\u0101 un mekl\u0113\u0161anas rezult\u0101tos aptuveni katru tre\u0161o reklam\u0113to sludin\u0101jumu lapas iel\u0101des reizi.*</li><li>Ja v\u0113l arvien redzat k\u013C\u016Bdu,<<CONTACTLINK>>sazinieties ar m\u016Bsu klientu apkalpo\u0161anas grupu<</CONTACTLINK>>.</li></ul>',
